c effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/108752/', '', 'Azelastine, Ketotifen, Promethazine', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Thiethylperazine, Trimethobenzamide, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole, Lidocaine, Tetracaine, More', 1767369485);
